J. Morris Foster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._Morris_Foster 0 J. Morris Foster (September 9, 1881 – April 24, 1966) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 79 films between 1914 and 1923. He was born in Foxbert, Pennsylvania and died in Burbank, California.
